org.goldenorb
Class OrbPartition

java.lang.Object
  org.goldenorb.jet.OrbPartitionMember
      org.goldenorb.OrbPartition
All Implemented Interfaces:
Runnable, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable, org.apache.hadoop.ipc.VersionedProtocol, OrbConfigurable, OrbPartitionCommunicationProtocol, OrbPartitionManagerProtocol, Member
public class OrbPartition
extends OrbPartitionMember
implements Runnable, OrbPartitionCommunicationProtocol, OrbPartitionManagerProtocol

OrbPartition, spawned from via OrbPartitionProcess, is responsible for loading input data, assigning file splits to other OrbPartition processes and coordinating with other OrbPartition processes via the exchange of Messages and Vertices. In addition to start up and coordination, OrbPartition processes are run responsible for stepping through the graph algorithms themselves, via the compute method.
